{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6288","heading":"Unfunded priorities of the Administration","label":"6288 Unfunded priorities of the Administration","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptVI/sptB/ch607/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in , War and National Defense, prior to repeal by .section 2756 of Title 50Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(b)(1)","Amendments2025—, realigned margins.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(B)Subsec. (b). , struck out pars. (1) and (2) headings which read as follows: “” and “”, respectively.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(A)In generalPrioritization of priorities"],"amendments":["Amendments2025—, realigned margins.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(B)Subsec. (b). , struck out pars. (1) and (2) headings which read as follows: “” and “”, respectively.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(A)In generalPrioritization of priorities"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Annual Report or Certification","label":"a .—Annual Report or Certification","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a report on the unfunded priorities of the Administration; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if the Administrator determines that there are no unfunded priorities to include in such a report, a certification and explanation by the Administrator, without delegation, of the determination.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Elements","label":"b .—Elements","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A summary description of that priority, including the objectives to be achieved or the risk to be mitigated if that priority is funded (whether in whole or in part).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The additional amount of funds recommended in connection with the objectives or risk mitigation under subparagraph (A).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Account information with respect to that priority.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each report under subsection (a)(1) shall present the unfunded priorities covered by the report in order of urgency of priority.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Unfunded Priority Defined","label":"c .—Unfunded Priority Defined","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is not funded in the budget of the President for that fiscal year as submitted to Congress pursuant to ;section 1105(a) of title 31","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is necessary to address a requirement associated with the mission of the Administration; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if additional resources were available for the budget to fund the program, activity, or mission requirement; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6288/c/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6288%2Fc%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of a program, activity, or mission requirement that emerged after the budget was formulated, if the program, activity, or mission requirement had emerged before the budget was formulated.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
